OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith some showers. Showers mainly over
OL,7,FShetland with drier and brighter
OL,8,Fspells for Orkney. Moderate to fresh
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fshowers, perhaps merging to longer
OL,13,Fspells of rain. Overnight, showers
OL,14,Fclearing south of Shetland, becoming
OL,15,Fconfined to Orkney. Moderate or fresh
OL,16,Fnorthwesterly winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
