OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FShowers clearing to the south
OL,6,Fof Orkney in the morning to leave a
OL,7,Fdry day with sunny spells for all
OL,8,Fareas. Light to moderate southeasterly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,13,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,14,FMostly cloudy but with some bright or
OL,15,Fsunny intervals breaking through at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
